437
00:20:51,020 --> 00:20:52,900
No idea who wrote this file.

438
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:55,040
This person must be good
at writing compositions.

439
00:20:55,180 --> 00:20:56,690
He can get full marks for presentation.

440
00:20:57,500 --> 00:20:59,530
Composing and writing
mean the same thing.

441
00:21:00,330 --> 00:21:01,500
Writing compositions?

442
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:03,060
Isn't the meaning

443
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:04,700
repeated?

444
00:21:04,820 --> 00:21:05,860
Ignore it.

445
00:21:05,860 --> 00:21:06,900
The point is

446
00:21:07,140 --> 00:21:08,820
his presentation is very neat.

447
00:21:08,820 --> 00:21:10,900
Ordinary people don't write articles
that carefully.

448
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:12,740
There will be some signs
of modification.

449
00:21:12,860 --> 00:21:13,860
But he didn't.

450
00:21:14,020 --> 00:21:15,540
As if it had been recopied.

451
00:21:21,740 --> 00:21:23,300
(Qingyang Cui Case)

452
00:21:23,300 --> 00:21:26,460
(To be punished by the death penalty.)

453
00:21:29,980 --> 00:21:32,180
(Cao Mansion)

454
00:21:32,180 --> 00:21:35,900
(Qingyang Cui Case)

