458
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:44,540
This is obviously a recopy.

459
00:21:45,660 --> 00:21:47,060
I was blinded by a single leaf.

460
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:49,240
I had been delving
into the contents of the file,

461
00:21:49,240 --> 00:21:50,100
yet I never expected

462
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:52,860
that the key information lay
beyond the words themselves.

463
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:55,740
The case was so urgent back then.

464
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:57,110
Yet Master Xiao still took the time

465
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:58,180
to copy it out deliberately

466
00:21:58,190 --> 00:22:01,040
and submit it to the Capital Prefecture
and the Court of Judicial Review.

467
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:02,880
He must have secrets
that must be kept hidden.

468
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:06,950
Unfortunately,

469
00:22:07,900 --> 00:22:09,900
Master Xiao is now in a coma.

470
00:22:10,200 --> 00:22:11,490
We can't get anything out of him.

471
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:15,380
Fifth Master Xiao

472
00:22:15,490 --> 00:22:18,300
is a taciturn person
who won't say a word.

473
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:21,340
However, he was very diligent
in writing.

474
00:22:21,340 --> 00:22:24,140
Not only would he carry a tablet
when attending court meetings,

475
00:22:24,140 --> 00:22:25,830
but even while eating or walking,

476
00:22:26,010 --> 00:22:27,850
he would bring different kinds of slips

477
00:22:28,300 --> 00:22:30,260
to record events that occurred.

478
00:22:30,620 --> 00:22:32,100
So some people made fun of him,

479
00:22:32,100 --> 00:22:34,220
saying he was no different
from those attendants

480
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:37,220
who constantly recorded the daily life
of His Majesty.

481
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:38,380
They gave him a nickname,

482
00:22:38,380 --> 00:22:40,220
Attendant Prince Consort.

483
00:22:41,650 --> 00:22:42,900
So I suppose

484
00:22:43,290 --> 00:22:44,740
when he was investigating the case,

485
00:22:44,980 --> 00:22:47,420
he would also carry a slip
to record events.

486
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:57,820
If Prince Consort Xiao

487
00:22:58,180 --> 00:23:00,620
left behind that slip,

488
00:23:01,260 --> 00:23:02,700
perhaps there will be new clues.

489
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:06,100
By the way,

490
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,850
