in their prime.

520
00:24:06,690 --> 00:24:08,460
Who could benefit from the case?

521
00:24:11,050 --> 00:24:12,820
If that were really the case,

522
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:14,510
Prince Zhao would certainly not want us

523
00:24:14,520 --> 00:24:16,070
to continue investigating.

524
00:24:16,310 --> 00:24:17,880
Even if there are many suspicious points

525
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,140
about Prince Zhao,

526
00:24:20,100 --> 00:24:21,560
