Zhao Xunzhi was a disciple
of the Capital Prefect.

846
00:35:12,330 --> 00:35:13,660
Why didn't he tell me?

847
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:15,540
He really was my father's disciple.

848
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:17,260
But after something happened
in my family,

849
00:35:17,260 --> 00:35:18,390
he wanted to avoid suspicion,

850
00:35:18,520 --> 00:35:19,720
so he never mentioned it again.

851
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:25,980
(Benefiting and Helping the People)

852
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:27,700
Sachets. Sachets.

853
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,660
Sachets with various scents.

854
00:35:29,700 --> 00:35:30,700
Lady, take a look.

855
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:31,560
I found out

856
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:35,220
Mr. Meng, Left Supervisor,

857
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,900
is quite worried
about his granddaughter's marriage.

858
00:35:38,460 --> 00:35:39,780
Mr. Meng also mentioned it to me.

859
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:43,060
- What's wrong, milady?
- Take a look.

860
00:35:43,060 --> 00:35:44,420
Do you have something on your mind?

861
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:45,700
No.

862
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,020
Not really.

863
00:35:47,260 --> 00:35:48,540
Why do you ask like that?

864
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:51,240
You seem absent-minded today.

865
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,270
It's fragrant.

866
00:35:52,590 --> 00:35:53,590
Lady, take a look.

867
00:35:55,740 --> 00:35:57,940
Alright, actually I read a novel.

868
00:35:57,940 --> 00:35:58,900
It's quite cruel.

869
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:01,340
Why are you reading that for no reason?

870
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,380
That stuff is so difficult.

871
00:36:02,380 --> 00:36:03,160
Can it not be cruel?

872
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:06,540
What are you saying?

873
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:08,580
I mean, I read

874
00:36:08,580 --> 00:36:09,860
a sad story.

875
00:36:11,340 --> 00:36:12,360
What story?

876
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:13,540
In the story,

877
00:36:13,940 --> 00:36:15,060
that lady

878
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:17,460
accidentally fell off a cliff.

879
00:36:17,690 --> 00:36:18,540
At this time,

880
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:20,580
a handsome young man came to rescue her.

881
00:36:20,580 --> 00:36:22,620
She thought, 'better you than me'.

882
00:36:22,620 --> 00:36:24,180
She didn't care if his arm was broken,

883
00:36:24,180 --> 00:36:25,780
as long as he could save her.

884
00:36:26,620 --> 00:36:28,680
This young lady is really heartless.

885
00:36:29,500 --> 00:36:30,340
Yes.

886
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:33,460
Despite being such a heartless person,

887
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:35,500
she was actually willing
to let herself fall

888
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:37,240
to save the life of the one
who rescued her.

889
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,940
Then she must really love that person.

890
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:40,140
No way, how could that be?

891
00:36:46,260 --> 00:36:47,140
It's not important.

892
00:36:47,140 --> 00:36:48,580
Anyway,

893
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:51,060
this lifesaver will eventually
marry someone else.

894
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:53,340
How can the story be like this?

895
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:55,940
That young lady will be sad.

896
00:36:55,940 --> 00:36:57,140
No, she is not sad.

897
00:36:57,140 --> 00:36:58,180
How could she be sad?

898
00:36:58,180 --> 00:36:59,380
This is too perverse.

899
00:37:00,080 --> 00:37:01,300
Milady, why are you so excited?

900
00:37:01,300 --> 00:37:02,550
What exactly do you want to say?

901
00:37:02,550 --> 00:37:03,540
Why can't I understand?

902
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:07,220
It's nothing.

903
00:37:08,020 --> 00:37:09,020
Really, it's nothing.

904
00:37:12,780 --> 00:37:16,740
(Yunshui Manor)

905
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:29,980
We're friends.

906
00:37:30,200 --> 00:37:31,420
How could you say you serve me?

907
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:34,540
Didn't you say before

908
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:36,220
that you don't plan to make friends?

909
00:37:38,660 --> 00:37:39,860
People change.

910
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:41,860
Then we are friends now.

911
00:37:42,380 --> 00:37:43,380
In Future Village,

912
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:45,700
friends should shake hands.

913
00:37:52,860 --> 00:37:53,740
Hold on to me.

914
00:37:54,340 --> 00:37:55,180
Don't let go.

915
00:38:15,980 --> 00:38:17,100
