So hard.)

916
00:38:17,100 --> 00:38:18,310
(For eating spicy food,
we risked our lives.)

917
00:38:18,310 --> 00:38:19,960
(All because there are
no chili peppers here.)

918
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:21,190
(If people in Yong'an wanna
eat something spicy,)

919
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:22,440
(they rely on Sichuan pepper, ginger,
, piper longum, and evodia fruit.)

920
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:23,380
(Some are actually quite expensive.)

921
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:24,720
(The smartweed we happened to find
while on the run)

922
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:26,280
