for making fermentation starter.)

923
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,480
(It's rarely eaten directly.)

924
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:29,240
(As soon as it entered my mouth,
that familiar stinging sensation...)

925
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:32,020
(I have come back to life.)

